'''愛德華·奧索克·門迪'''（{{lang-fr|'''Édouard Osoque Mendy'''}}，{{bd|1992年|3月1日}}），是一名[[塞內加爾|塞內加爾]]職業足球員，司職[[守門員|守門員]]，現效力[[英超|英超]]俱樂部[[切爾西足球俱樂部|切爾西]]，并代表[[塞內加爾國家足球隊|塞内加尔国家队]]参加国际比赛。

== 俱樂部生涯 ==
=== 早年生涯 ===
門迪在13歲時加入[[勒阿弗爾競技俱樂部|勒阿弗爾]]的青訓系統<ref name=5things>{{cite web |title=Édouard Mendy: 5 things on the Rennes and Senegal goalkeeper |url=https://www.ligue1.com/Articles/NEWS/2020/08/31/edouard-mendy-5-things-on-the-rennes-and-senegal-goalkeeper |publisher=Ligue de Football Professionnel |date=31 August 2020 |access-date=2021-02-22 |archive-date=2020-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200925132858/https://www.ligue1.com/Articles/NEWS/2020/08/31/edouard-mendy-5-things-on-the-rennes-and-senegal-goalkeeper |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但在多方面都被{{link-en|扎克列·鲍彻|Zacharie Boucher}}壓下來之下，他決定前往CS勒阿弗爾（CS Municipaux Le Havre）的青年軍<ref name=5things/>。2011年，門迪在[[法丙|法丙]]俱樂部{{link-en|科唐坦地區瑟堡體育俱樂部|AS Cherbourg Football|瑟堡}}開始其職業生涯，並在那裡效力了三年，總共上陣26場，之後的一年則為自由身<ref>{{cite web |title=Mendy 'had doubts' during unemployment |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/54652205 |website=BBC Sport |access-date=22 October 2020 |date=22 October 2020 |archive-date=2020-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201222947/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/54652205 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他在2020年接受《[[運動畫刊|運動畫刊]]》訪問時表示：「我是真的對是否該繼續下去抱有疑問」<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|agency=Associated Press|title=Six Years After Being Without a Club, Edouard Mendy Is Chelsea's GK Savior|url=https://www.si.com/soccer/2020/10/23/edouard-mendy-chelsea-gk-career|access-date=2020-12-31|website=[[運動畫刊|Sports Illustrated]]|language=en-us|archive-date=2020-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124043355/https://www.si.com/soccer/2020/10/23/edouard-mendy-chelsea-gk-career|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在22歲時，門迪正式向政府登記無業，並開始尋找足球以外的工作<ref name=":0" />。然而在2015年，門迪在朋友兼前隊友{{link-en|泰德·拉維|Ted Lavie}}的引線下，得到填補[[馬賽奧林匹克|馬賽]]守門員空缺的機會。在與其守門員教練多米尼克·伯納托維茲（Dominique Bernatowicz）通電話後，他正式成為該隊的第四門將<ref>{{Cite news|title=From being unemployed to joining Chelsea - Mendy's downs and ups|language=en-GB|work=BBC Sport|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/africa/54085178|access-date=2020-12-31|archive-date=2020-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101104831/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/africa/54085178|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並在2015–16球季列進馬賽的預備隊內，作{{link-en|弗洛里安·埃斯卡爾|Florian Escales}}的後備<ref name=5things/>。

=== 蘭斯 ===
為了得到穩定的上場時間，門迪在2016–17球季加盟當時仍在[[法乙|法乙]]的[[蘭斯體育會|蘭斯]]<ref name=5things/>。在開季首場時，他在首發門將{{link-en|約翰·卡拉索|Johann Carrasso}}於5分鐘被紅牌出場的情況下替補亮相，助球隊以1-1戰平[[艾米恩斯體育會|艾米恩斯]]。門迪在此後的七場比賽中有三場成功力保不失<ref name=5things/>。下個球季，他的先發地位首次未被動搖，他在34場比賽中有18場保持不失球<ref>{{cite web |url=http://stade-de-reims.com/ensemble-fetons-nos-champions/ |title=Ensemble, fêtons nos champions ! – Stade de Reims |publisher=Stade de Reims |date=7 May 2018 |access-date=11 May 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180512112428/http://stade-de-reims.com/ensemble-fetons-nos-champions/ |archive-date=12 May 2018}}</ref>，除了為蘭斯奪得法乙冠軍外，還幫助他們重返暌違一年半的[[法甲|法甲]]<ref name="5things" />。在2018–19球季，門迪為蘭斯上陣了38場聯賽，有14場力保不失，為該球季的「銅手套」，並助球隊取得第8位，為他們在法甲的歷史新高<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=Scouting Report: Édouard Mendy|url=https://breakingthelines.com/scouting-report/scouting-report-edouard-mendy/|access-date=2021-01-01|website=Breaking The Lines|language=en-GB|archive-date=2020-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201205085135/https://breakingthelines.com/scouting-report/scouting-report-edouard-mendy/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 雷恩 ===
2019年8月6日，[[雷恩足球俱乐部|雷恩]]宣佈簽下門迪，據傳費用約為400萬歐元，以取代轉會至[[德甲|德甲]][[奧格斯堡足球俱樂部|奧格斯堡]]的原門將[[托馬斯·高比克|托馬什·庫貝克]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.staderennais.com/edouard-mendy-nouveau-gardien-du-stade-rennais-fc |title=Édouard Mendy nouveau gardien du Stade Rennais F.C. |publisher=Stade Rennais F.C. |language=fr |access-date=6 August 2019 |archive-date=2020-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200925132903/https://www.staderennais.com/edouard-mendy-nouveau-gardien-du-stade-rennais-fc/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-11-03|title=Chelsea can thank Cech for Mendy arrival and Rennes may pay the price|url=https://www.espn.com/soccer/chelsea/story/4224729/chelsea-can-thank-cech-for-mendy-arrival-and-rennes-may-pay-the-price|access-date=2021-01-01|website=ESPN.com|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120135519/https://www.espn.com/soccer/chelsea/story/4224729/chelsea-can-thank-cech-for-mendy-arrival-and-rennes-may-pay-the-price|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他在同月25日對上[[斯特拉斯堡競賽會|斯特拉斯堡]]的比賽中首次亮相，並救下一球[[罰點球|點球]]，助球隊以2–0在客場[[梅瑙球場|梅瑙球場]]零封對手<ref name="5things" />。最終門迪在2019–20球季上陣25場，其中9場保持不失球，為雷恩得以在這因[[2019冠狀病毒病法國疫情|COVID-19疫情]]而腰斬的賽季中取得季軍，並得到參加[[歐冠|歐冠]]資格的功臣之一<ref name=":1" />。

=== 切爾西 ===
2020年9月24日，[[切爾西足球俱樂部|切爾西]]宣佈他們已經與門迪簽下一份為期五年的合同，據稱轉會費達到2200萬英鎊<ref>{{Cite web|title=Chelsea transfer news: Edouard Mendy makes Chelsea move|url=https://www.chelseafc.com/en/news/2020/09/24/mendy-makes-chelsea-move|publisher=Chelsea F.C.|access-date=24 September 2020|archive-date=2020-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200924092309/https://www.chelseafc.com/en/news/2020/09/24/mendy-makes-chelsea-move|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.skysports.com/football/news/11668/12068937/edouard-mendy-chelsea-sign-goalkeeper-from-rennes-for-22m-on-five-year-deal |title=Chelsea sign goalkeeper from Rennes for £22m on five-year deal |date=24 September 2020 |website=Sky Sports |access-date=24 September 2020 |archive-date=2020-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200925132913/https://www.skysports.com/football/news/11668/12068937/edouard-mendy-chelsea-sign-goalkeeper-from-rennes-for-22m-on-five-year-deal/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。時任主帥[[法蘭克·蘭帕德|法蘭克·蘭帕德]]透露隊內的退休名將兼現任技術顧問[[佩特·切赫|佩特·切赫]]在此次交易中起到關鍵的作用<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.skysports.com/football/news/11668/12078674/edouard-mendy-to-chelsea-frank-lampard-says-petr-cech-had-big-say-in-deal-for-rennes-goalkeeper |title=Frank Lampard says Petr Cech had 'big say' in deal for Rennes goalkeeper |date=22 September 2020 |website=Sky Sports |access-date=24 September 2020 |archive-date=2020-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200925132916/https://www.skysports.com/football/news/11668/12078674/edouard-mendy-to-chelsea-frank-lampard-says-petr-cech-had-big-say-in-deal-for-rennes-goalkeeper/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。五日後，門迪在對上[[托特纳姆热刺足球俱乐部|托特纳姆热刺]]的[[2020年至2021年英格蘭聯賽盃|聯賽盃]]第四輪比賽中首次登場，惜球隊在1–1戰平後在[[互射十二碼|互射十二碼]]時以4–5敗北<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.goal.com/en/news/chelsea-boss-lampard-pleased-with-mendy-debut-despite/1b5okfmzlkfbd14h8fmnnnuo24 |title=Chelsea boss Lampard pleased with Mendy debut despite Carabao Cup exit |date=29 September 2020 |website=Goal.com |access-date=29 September 2020 |archive-date=2020-11-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201103203754/https://www.goal.com/en/news/chelsea-boss-lampard-pleased-with-mendy-debut-despite/1b5okfmzlkfbd14h8fmnnnuo24 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。其[[英超|英超]]首秀方面則出現在2020年10月3日對上[[水晶宮足球俱樂部|水晶宮]]的比賽中，並助切爾西贈送四蛋予對手<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/54305844 |title=Chelsea 4–0 Crystal Palace |date=3 October 2020 |website=BBC Sport |access-date=3 October 2020 |archive-date=2020-10-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201028053759/https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/54305844 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。同月31日，他在對陣[[伯恩利足球俱乐部|伯恩利]]時再次零封，助球隊以3–0力克對方，自此成為自2004年的切赫後，首位在頭三場英超比賽中都保持不失球的切爾西守門員<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://twitter.com/Squawka/status/1322583334023823361 |title=Edouard Mendy is the first Chelsea goalkeeper to keep a clean sheet in their first three Premier League games since Petr Čech in 2004. They’ve found a gem.💎 |date=31 October 2020 |publisher=Squawka Football |website=Twitter |access-date=31 October 2020 |archive-date=2020-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031165717/https://twitter.com/Squawka/status/1322583334023823361 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在歐冠分組賽對上舊東家雷恩時，門迪再次力保不失，除了再度令球隊取得3–0的賽果外，也使得「藍軍」十年來首次連續五場完封<ref>{{cite web|url=https://weaintgotnohistory.sbnation.com/2020/11/5/21550619/cech-recommended-mendy-above-30-40-others-in-chelseas-1-5-year-long-goalkeeper-search|title=Čech recommended Mendy above 30-40 others in Chelsea’s 1.5-year-long goalkeeper search|website=SB Nation|date=5 November 2020|access-date=5 November 2020|archive-date=2020-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120220150/https://weaintgotnohistory.sbnation.com/2020/11/5/21550619/cech-recommended-mendy-above-30-40-others-in-chelseas-1-5-year-long-goalkeeper-search|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

門迪是英超現時唯一一位為非洲國家隊效力的守門員，也是繼[[2011–12賽季英格蘭超級聯賽|2011–12球季]]為[[狼隊|狼隊]]和[[尼日利亞國家足球隊|尼日利亞]]效力的{{link-en|卡爾·伊克梅|Carl Ikeme}}後的首位<ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-09-24|title=Mendy: The 4th African Goalkeeper To Join Premier League|url=https://the-sportsnation.com/2020/09/24/mendy-the-4th-african-goalkeeper-to-join-premier-league/|access-date=2021-01-01|website=The SportsNation|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123045629/https://the-sportsnation.com/2020/09/24/mendy-the-4th-african-goalkeeper-to-join-premier-league/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 國家隊生涯 ==
門迪於1992年3月1日出生於[[法國|法國]][[濱海塞納省|濱海塞納省]][[蒙蒂維利耶|蒙蒂維利耶]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.worldfootball.net/player_summary/edouard-mendy/ |title=Edouard Mendy: Profile |website=worldfootball.net |publisher=HEIM:SPIEL |access-date=22 October 2020 |archive-date=2020-11-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201119043452/https://www.worldfootball.net/player_summary/edouard-mendy/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，父親為[[幾內亞比紹|幾內亞比紹]]裔，母親則有著塞內加爾血統，因此有著代表法國、幾內亞比紹和塞內加爾的資格。2016年11月，他被[[幾內亞比紹國家足球隊|幾內亞比紹國家隊]]徵召參加對上[[葡超|葡超]]球隊[[比蘭倫斯SAD|比蘭倫斯]]和[[埃斯托里爾足球俱樂部|埃斯托里爾]]的[[友賽|友賽]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.soudjurtu.com/2016/11/djurtus-lista-de-convocados-do-para-o.html|title=Djurtus: Lista de convocados do para o amistoso com Belenenses e Estoril|date=12 November 2016|access-date=23 July 2018|language=pt|publisher=Sou Djurtu|archive-date=2018-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180724002310/http://www.soudjurtu.com/2016/11/djurtus-lista-de-convocados-do-para-o.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。當時門迪的父親患了重病，離逝世僅咫尺之遙，因此他有意達成其父的意願，答應幾國國家隊的邀請<ref name=GSF>{{Cite web|url=https://www.galsenfoot.com/stade-de-reims-edouard-mendy-senegal-choix-a-toujours-ete-de-representer-cette-selection/|title=Stade de Reims- Edouard Mendy : "Le Sénégal ? Mon choix a toujours été de représenter cette sélection"|date=17 November 2017|access-date=23 July 2018|language=fr|publisher=Galsenfoot|quote=I was contacted by Guinea (Guinea-Bissau), it goes back to last winter (2016). I could have participated in the (2017) African Cup of Nations, but I finally declined this proposal. I was a little rushed to mention this possibility, I went through a personal period a little complicated, I almost lost my father, of Guinean (Bissau-Guinean) origin, who was very sick. This decision was to pleasure him, not really my choice. I have always wanted to represent Senegal, my mother's homeland. In difficult moments, we do not always take the necessary time for reflection and therefore not always the right decisions.|archive-date=2019-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191209225754/https://www.galsenfoot.com/stade-de-reims-edouard-mendy-senegal-choix-a-toujours-ete-de-representer-cette-selection/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。不久之後，門迪入選幾內亞比紹的[[2017年非洲國家盃|2017年非洲國家盃]]初選名單<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.football365.fr/can-2017-guinee-bissau-premiere-liste-de-35-joueurs-2857450.html|title=CAN 2017 – Guinée-Bissau : Une Première liste de 35 joueurs|date=19 December 2016|publisher=Football 365|access-date=23 July 2018|language=fr|archive-date=2016-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220042046/http://www.football365.fr/can-2017-guinee-bissau-premiere-liste-de-35-joueurs-2857450.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但他最終婉拒該徵召，並選擇代表[[塞內加爾國家足球隊|塞內加爾]]<ref name=GSF/>。

門迪在2018年11月18日以1-0擊敗[[赤道畿內亞國家足球隊|赤道畿內亞]]的比賽中首次代表塞內加爾<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://taaye.com/senegal/edward-mendy-the-competition-between-us-is-healthy/|title=Edward Mendy: "The competition between us is healthy"|access-date=2021-02-22|archive-date=2020-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200925155821/https://taaye.com/senegal/edward-mendy-the-competition-between-us-is-healthy//|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。他之後在[[2019年非洲國家盃|2019年非洲國家盃]]中成為國家隊的一號門將，門迪在分組賽頭兩場皆有上陣，而球隊則分別以2–0擊敗[[坦尚尼亞國家足球隊|坦尚尼亞]]和以0–1敗給[[阿爾及利亞國家足球隊|阿爾及利亞]]。然而在分組賽的最後一場比賽中，他在熱身時弄傷手指退出陣容，最終「特蘭加雄獅」在決賽中以1–0敗給阿爾及利亞<ref>{{Cite web|title=Afcon 2019: Senegal's Edouard Mendy ruled out of the rest of competition {{!}} Goal.com|url=https://www.goal.com/en-us/news/senegals-mendy-ruled-out-of-the-rest-of-africa-cup-of/80ohdi9p6s821cj6la1502o7q#:~:text=Senegal%20goalkeeper%20Edouard%20Mendy%20has,game%20against%20Kenya%20on%20Monday.|access-date=2021-01-01|website=www.goal.com|archive-date=2022-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220504042813/https://www.goal.com/en-us/news/senegals-mendy-ruled-out-of-the-rest-of-africa-cup-of/80ohdi9p6s821cj6la1502o7q#:~:text=Senegal%20goalkeeper%20Edouard%20Mendy%20has,game%20against%20Kenya%20on%20Monday.}}</ref>。

[[2021年非洲國家盃|2021年非洲國家盃]]，門迪代表的塞內加爾繼上屆再次打進冠軍賽，互射十二碼以4-2擊敗[[埃及國家足球隊|埃及]]，首度稱王，他也獲得賽事的最佳守門員獎。

== 踢球風格 ==
門迪被認為是一位在大部分比賽中身材都佔優勢的守門員，能在球場下半區起到顯著的防守作用<ref name=":1" />。在2019–20於雷恩效力時，他的撲救成功率達到75.3%，平均每場比賽救下2.5球，為當季法甲中最好，同時也保有40碼內達51.4%的傳球成功率，與有著出色腳法，現效力[[曼彻斯特城足球俱乐部|曼城]]的[[艾達臣·摩拉斯|艾達臣]]的數據相同<ref>{{Cite web|last=Nalton|first=James|date=2017-12-19|title=The Ederson Effect: The Story of a Goal Kick|url=https://worldfootballindex.com/2017/12/ederson-goal-kicks-tactics-manchester-city-brazil/|access-date=2021-01-01|website=World Football Index|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124062554/https://worldfootballindex.com/2017/12/ederson-goal-kicks-tactics-manchester-city-brazil/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。門迪的踢法果敢，時常離開門線，出擊接下橫傳。他在球場上也非常善於表達，經常組織後衛們的位置<ref name=":1" /><ref>{{Cite web|title=Who is Edouard Mendy? Strengths and weaknesses of Chelsea's new number one|url=https://www.whoscored.com/Articles/QfsOf7YLq0atGnWbho1cyA/Show/Who-is-Edouard-Mendy-Strengths-and-weaknesses-of-Chelseas-new-number-one|access-date=2021-01-01|website=www.whoscored.com|archive-date=2020-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201022040839/https://www.whoscored.com/Articles/QfsOf7YLq0atGnWbho1cyA/Show/Who-is-Edouard-Mendy-Strengths-and-weaknesses-of-Chelseas-new-number-one|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在加盟切爾西後，時任主帥蘭帕德讚揚他有著積極的態度，並表示：「他（門迪）的性格看似很隨和，但訓練時卻有著強硬的一面。他很容易就能維持自己的良好狀態，也渴望與隊友們和我交流。他的臉上總是帶著微笑，一進到更衣室便準備好隨時在球場內奔跑，這對其他球員來說真的起到一個非常正面的作用」<ref>{{Cite web|title=‘He has a smile on his face and a great work ethic’ - Lampard discusses Mendy|url=https://www.chelseafc.com/en/news/2020/11/03/-he-has-a-smile-on-his-face-and-a-great-work-ethic---lampard-dis|date=2020-11-03|access-date=2021-01-01|website=chelseafc.com|archive-date=2020-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201130105739/https://www.chelseafc.com/en/news/2020/11/03/-he-has-a-smile-on-his-face-and-a-great-work-ethic---lampard-dis|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

